    "AWS region for the Bedrock runtime endpoint.": "Bedrock 运行时端点的 AWS 区域。",
    "Ability for Claude to remember personal context from your team members' chats to make conversations more relevant. When off, each conversation starts fresh with no cross-session context.": "让 Claude 记住团队成员聊天中的个人背景信息，使对话更具相关性。关闭时，每次对话都会重新开始，不带任何跨会话的上下文。",
    "Ability for Claude to run code, create documents (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, PDF), and access network resources within conversations.": "让 Claude 能够在对话中运行代码、创建文档（Word、Excel、PowerPoint、PDF）以及访问网络资源。",
