    "Claude Code CLI": "Claude Code CLI",
    "Claude Code Desktop already enforces your <link>Managed settings</link> and MDM-deployed configuration. These legacy toggles will be retired in an upcoming release. To keep an existing restriction in effect, set <code>permissions.disableBypassPermissionsMode</code> and <code>disableAutoMode</code> to <code>{value}</code> in Managed settings or via MDM.": "Claude Code Desktop 已强制执行你的<link>托管设置</link>和通过 MDM 部署的配置。这些旧版开关将在即将发布的版本中停用。若要保持现有限制生效，请在托管设置中或通过 MDM 将 <code>permissions.disableBypassPermissionsMode</code> 和 <code>disableAutoMode</code> 设置为 <code>{value}</code>。",
    "Claude Code Desktop already enforces your <link>Managed settings</link> and MDM-deployed configuration. This legacy toggle will be retired in an upcoming release. To keep an existing restriction in effect, set <code>permissions.disableBypassPermissionsMode</code> to <code>{value}</code> in Managed settings or via MDM.": "Claude Code Desktop 已经强制执行你的 <link>Managed 设置</link> 和 MDM 部署的配置。此旧版开关将在即将发布的版本中被移除。如需让现有限制继续生效，请在 Managed 设置中或通过 MDM 将 <code>permissions.disableBypassPermissionsMode</code> 设置为 <code>{value}</code>。",
    "Claude Code Desktop has been disabled by your organization's device management policy.": "桌面端 Claude Code 已被您组织的设备管理政策禁用。",
    "Claude Code Desktop respects your organization's <link>Managed settings</link> and any MDM-deployed managed settings, the same as Claude Code in the CLI and IDE.": "Claude Code Desktop 会遵循你所在组织的<link>托管设置</link>以及任何通过 MDM 部署的托管设置，与 CLI 和 IDE 中的 Claude Code 相同。",
