    "Cowork on Windows requires a machine with x64 support. Windows on Arm based machines are not currently supported. (Coming Soon)": "Windows 版 Cowork 需要支持 x64 的机器。目前尚不支持基于 Arm 的 Windows 机器（即将推出）。",
