    "Members are added manually via email invitation.": "成员通过电子邮件邀请手动添加。",
    "Members are assigned to one role based on IdP group membership on each sync. If their IdP groups map to multiple roles, the first role in the table below applies. Members not in a mapped group are removed from the organization.": "每次同步时，成员会根据其 IdP 群组成员身份被分配到一个角色。如果他们的 IdP 群组映射到多个角色，则以下表中的第一个角色为准。不在任何已映射群组中的成员将被移出组织。",
    "Members are assigned to one role based on IdP group membership when they sign in. If their IdP groups map to multiple roles, the first role in the table below applies. Members not in a mapped group are removed from the organization.": "成员登录时会根据其 IdP 群组成员资格被分配到一个角色。如果他们的 IdP 群组映射到多个角色，则适用下表中的第一个角色。不在映射群组中的成员将被移出组织。",
    "Members are automatically provisioned when they sign in with SSO.": "成员通过 SSO 登录时会自动预置。",
    "Members are synced from your identity provider upfront.": "成员会预先从你的身份提供商同步。",
    "Members can still switch models themselves, and their choice sticks.": "成员仍然可以自行切换模型，并且他们的选择会保留。",
    "Members from groups": "来自群组的成员",
    "Members in your organization may need to sign in again. Sessions older than the selected duration will end immediately, and active sessions will be shortened.": "您组织中的成员可能需要重新登录。早于所选时长的会话将立即结束，活动会话将被缩短。",
    "Members in {count, plural, one {this group} other {these groups}} will fall back to their seat-tier default spend limit.": "{count, plural, one {该群组} other {这些群组}}中的成员将回退到其席位层级的默认消费限额。",
    "Members must have an @{domain} email address.": "成员必须拥有 @{domain} 邮箱地址。",
    "Members must have an {domains} email address.": "成员必须拥有 {domains} 电子邮件地址。",
    "Members on usage-based seats can't access Claude until this is turned on.": "在开启此项前，使用按需付费席位的成员将无法访问 Claude。",
    "Members to update": "要更新的成员",
    "Members who are not found in your identity provider will be removed from all organizations using SCIM provisioning.": "在你的身份提供商中找不到的成员，将从所有使用 SCIM 配置的组织中移除。",
    "Members who are not found in your identity provider will be removed from this organization.": "在您的身份提供商中找不到的成员将被从该组织中移除。",
    "Members with usage-based seats cannot use Claude until extra usage is enabled.": "在开启额外用量前，使用“按量计费”席位的成员无法使用 Claude。",
    "Membership for this group is managed by your identity provider. To add or remove members, update the group in your IdP. <link>Manage SCIM settings</link>": "此群组的成员资格由您的身份提供方管理。要添加或移除成员，请在您的 IdP 中更新该群组。<link>管理 SCIM 设置</link>",
