    "Only Claude accounts in your enterprise can connect supported connectors using an email on your verified domains. Contact support to request additional connectors.": "只有你企业中的 Claude 账户才能使用你已验证域名下的邮箱连接受支持的连接器。如需额外的连接器，请联系支持团队。",
    "Only Google Docs are supported at this time": "目前仅支持 Google 文档",
    "Only PNG, JPEG, GIF, and WebP images are supported.": "仅支持 PNG、JPEG、GIF 和 WebP 图片。",
