    "Per-tier spend limits become available after your trial converts to a paid plan.": "按层级的支出限制将在试用转为付费套餐后可用。",
    "Per-tool approval policy. \"ask\" requires user approval before each call; \"allow\" is the default. Use Disabled built-in tools to remove a tool entirely.": "按工具的批准策略。“ask”要求在每次调用前获得用户批准；“allow”是默认值。使用“禁用内置工具”可彻底移除某个工具。",
    "Per-user attribution on risky commands requires recent Claude Code client telemetry; older clients show aggregate counts only.": "高风险命令的按用户归因需要较新的 Claude Code 客户端遥测；较旧的客户端仅显示汇总计数。",
    "Per-user soft cap, counted client-side over the duration below. Not a server-enforced quota.": "每个用户的软上限，在客户端按下方时长统计。并非服务器强制执行的配额。",
