    "Pull requests": "拉取请求 (PR)",
    "Pull the latest earnings transcript and 10-Q for a target, extract guidance and key KPIs, compare to last quarter, and build a comps table against peers. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "拉取某个目标公司最新的财报电话会议记录和 10-Q，提取业绩指引和关键 KPI，与上一季度进行比较，并构建一张与同行对比的可比公司表。从我已连接的工具中拉取数据。如果缺少某个来源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Pull together a customer feedback digest — themes with counts, a few quotes, and what to prioritize. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "汇总一份客户反馈摘要 — 包含主题及计数、几条引述，以及应优先处理的事项。从我已连接的工具中拉取数据。如果缺少某个来源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Pull together a customer feedback digest — themes with counts, a few quotes, and what to prioritize. Show me what it looks like with sample feedback first. We can connect Slack and my support tool later.": "整理一份客户反馈摘要——带计数的主题、几条引述，以及应优先处理的事项。先用示例反馈给我展示一下效果。我们之后可以连接 Slack 和我的支持工具。",
    "Pull together a weekly read on what people are saying about us across surveys, social, press, and call transcripts. Cluster the themes, count the mentions, flag the sentiment, and tell me what to act on. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "汇总一份每周解读，了解人们在调研、社交媒体、新闻和通话记录中对我们的评价。归类主题、统计提及次数、标注情感倾向，并告诉我应采取哪些行动。从我已连接的工具中拉取数据。如果缺少某个来源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Pull together a weekly read on what people are saying about us across surveys, social, press, and call transcripts. Cluster the themes, count the mentions, flag the sentiment, and tell me what to act on. Show me a sample first. We can connect my sources later.": "汇总一份每周解读，了解人们在调研、社交媒体、新闻和通话记录中对我们的评价。归类主题、统计提及次数、标注情感倾向，并告诉我应采取哪些行动。先给我看个示例。我们之后可以连接我的来源。",
    "Pull weekly metrics and flag anything strange": "提取每周指标并标记任何异常情况",
