    "Put Claude to work on tasks while you step away. <link>Cowork</link> is now available on Pro as a research preview.": "当你离开时，让 Claude 处理任务。<link>Cowork</link> 现在在 Pro 版中作为研究预览版提供。",
    "Put Claude to work on tasks while you step away. <link>Cowork</link> is now available on Pro.": "当你离开时，让 Claude 继续处理任务。<link>Cowork</link> 现已在 Pro 方案中提供。",
    "Put together a customer-ready QBR deck — pull recent news on the account, work it into the slides, end with a recommendation. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "整理一份可直接呈现给客户的 QBR 演示文稿——获取该客户的近期新闻，将其融入幻灯片，并以一条建议作结。从我已连接的工具中获取数据。如果缺少数据源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Put together a customer-ready QBR deck — pull recent news on the account, work it into the slides, end with a recommendation. Show me one for a sample account first. We can add my template and call notes later.": "整理一份可直接面向客户的 QBR 演示文稿——提取该客户的近期新闻，融入幻灯片，最后给出一项建议。先用一个示例客户给我展示一份。我们之后可以添加我的模板和通话记录。",
    "Put together a one-pager I can read before a client meeting — who's coming, recent emails, what's new at their company, what to bring up. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "整理一份我可以在客户会议前阅读的单页文档——谁会出席、近期邮件、他们公司的最新动态、需要提出的要点。从我已连接的工具中提取数据。如果缺少来源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Put together a one-pager I can read before a client meeting — who's coming, recent emails, what's new at their company, what to bring up. Show me one for a sample meeting first. We can connect Gmail and my calendar later to run it every morning.": "整理一份我可以在客户会议前阅读的单页文档——谁会出席、近期邮件、他们公司的最新动态、需要提出的要点。先用一个示例会议给我展示一份。我们之后可以连接 Gmail 和我的日历，让它每天早晨运行。",
