    "Set up SMS": "设置短信",
    "Set up a Monday morning command center — a tiled dashboard with cards for my action items, emails I haven't replied to, and meetings that need prep. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "搭建一个周一早晨的指挥中心——一个平铺式仪表板，包含我的待办事项、尚未回复的邮件以及需要准备的会议等卡片。从我已连接的工具中获取数据。如果缺少某个数据源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Set up a Monday morning command center — a tiled dashboard with cards for my action items, emails I haven't replied to, and meetings that need prep. Show me what it looks like with a sample week first. We can connect Slack, Gmail, and my calendar later to run it every Monday.": "搭建一个周一早晨指挥中心——一个平铺式仪表板，包含我的待办事项、我尚未回复的邮件以及需要准备的会议卡片。先用一个示例周向我展示它的样子。之后我们可以连接 Slack、Gmail 和我的日历，让它每周一运行。",
    "Set up a Team plan": "设置团队计划",
    "Set up a campaign performance dashboard — spend, CPA, and conversions vs goal by channel and creative, plus a 'top performers' cut and a 'needs attention' cut. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "搭建一个营销活动绩效仪表板 — 按渠道和创意展示支出、CPA 和转化对比目标的情况，外加“表现最佳”和“需要关注”两个切分视图。从我已连接的工具中拉取数据。如果缺少某个来源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Set up a campaign performance dashboard — spend, CPA, and conversions vs goal by channel and creative, plus a 'top performers' cut and a 'needs attention' cut. Use some sample campaigns to start. We can paste in my numbers or connect my ad accounts later.": "搭建一个广告活动效果仪表板——按渠道和创意展示花费、CPA 以及转化与目标的对比，外加一个“表现最佳”视图和一个“需要关注”视图。先用一些示例广告活动开始。之后我们可以粘贴我的数据或连接我的广告账户。",
    "Set up a cloud container": "设置云容器",
    "Set up a new folder with instructions and files.": "设置一个新文件夹，包含说明和文件。",
    "Set up a pipeline dashboard — stages, pipeline value over time, and what needs attention this week. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "搭建一个销售管道仪表板——展示各阶段、管道价值随时间的变化，以及本周需要关注的事项。从我已连接的工具中获取数据。如果缺少数据源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Set up a pipeline dashboard — stages, pipeline value over time, and what needs attention this week. Use some made-up deals to start. We can connect to my CRM or my own pipeline file later.": "设置一个销售管道仪表板 — 包括各阶段、随时间变化的管道价值，以及本周需要关注的事项。先用一些虚构的交易开始。我们稍后可以连接到我的 CRM 或我自己的管道文件。",
    "Set up a product metrics dashboard": "设置产品指标仪表板",
    "Set up a product metrics dashboard — DAU/WAU, weekly retention, funnel conversion, feature adoption, plus a quick read on the trends. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "搭建一个产品指标仪表板——DAU/WAU、每周留存率、漏斗转化率、功能采用率，外加对趋势的快速解读。从我已连接的工具中获取数据。如果缺少数据源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Set up a product metrics dashboard — DAU/WAU, weekly retention, funnel conversion, feature adoption, plus a quick read on the trends. Use sample data first. We can connect my analytics or send an export later to make it real.": "搭建一个产品指标仪表板 — DAU/WAU、周留存、漏斗转化、功能采用率，以及对趋势的快速解读。先使用示例数据。我们之后可以连接我的分析数据或发送导出文件以使其真实化。",
    "Set up a project tracker": "设置项目跟踪器",
    "Set up a project with files and context": "设置包含文件和上下文的项目",
    "Set up a revenue dashboard — top-line trend, top customers, segment mix, and forecast vs actual. Pull the data from my connected tools. If you're missing a source, ask before building.": "设置一个营收仪表板——总营收趋势、头部客户、细分组合，以及预测对比实际。从我已连接的工具中提取数据。如果缺少来源，请在构建前询问。",
    "Set up a revenue dashboard — top-line trend, top customers, segment mix, and forecast vs actual. Use sample data first. We can connect my warehouse or send an export later to make it real.": "搭建一个营收仪表板——展示总营收趋势、重点客户、细分构成，以及预测与实际的对比。先用示例数据。之后我们可以连接我的数据仓库或发送导出文件，使其成为真实数据。",
