    "The BAA also covers your use of the Anthropic API and Claude Code with ZDR (for qualifying organizations). Those services are configured separately. Contact your account team to enable HIPAA with other Eligible Services.": "BAA 还涵盖您对 Anthropic API 以及带 ZDR 的 Claude Code 的使用（适用于符合条件的组织）。这些服务需单独配置。请联系您的客户团队，以便对其他合格服务启用 HIPAA。",
    "The Claude Code GitHub App isn't installed on this repository. Install it to enable scanning.": "Claude Code GitHub App 未安装在此仓库上。安装它以启用扫描。",
