    "You can now turn chat on or off for your organization. Disabling chat also disables projects and artifacts.": "你现在可以为你的组织开启或关闭聊天。禁用聊天也会禁用项目和工件。",
    "You can only add members of your organization": "您只能添加您组织的成员",
