    "You've reached your {period, select, daily {daily } weekly {weekly } monthly {monthly } other {}}spend limit. Request more to keep going now.": "你已达到{period, select, daily {每日} weekly {每周} monthly {每月} other {}}消费限额。立即请求更多额度以继续。",
