    "Your Claude Fluency": "您的 Claude 熟练度",
    "Your Claude {tier} plan is good through {endDate}.": "您的 Claude {tier} 方案有效期至 {endDate}。",
    "Your Frame deploys. Click a card to open it in your browser.": "你的 Frame 已部署。点击卡片即可在浏览器中打开。",
