    "Your display name": "您的显示名称",
    "Your downgrade to the {planType} plan is scheduled for {downgradeDate}.": "您降级到 {planType} 方案的计划定于 {downgradeDate}。",
    "Your edits are suggestions": "您的编辑仅作为建议内容",
