    "Your organization has unlimited seats. Contact support to add other seat tiers.": "你的组织拥有无限席位。联系客服以添加其他席位等级。",
    "Your organization has unlimited seats. Contact support to add other seat types.": "您的组织拥有无限席位。请联系支持以添加其他席位类型。",
