    "Your seat type doesn't include usage credits. Manage spend limit to keep going now.": "你的席位类型不包含用量额度。请管理消费限额以立即继续。",
    "Your server was saved but not yet submitted for review. You can keep editing and submit from the detail page.": "您的服务器已保存，但尚未提交审核。您可以继续编辑，并从详情页面提交。",
